title: SPY + TSL + EVO
description: SPY teamed up with Push from The Seventh Letter to provide a facelift on the wall of Pacific Northwest retailer EVO to spice up the neighborhood. The piece currently graces the west side wall at the corner of 2nd and 36th Streets in Seattle, home of EVO's retail showroom. Check out the continuing collaboration between SPY and The Seventh Letter over at www.spyoptic.com/collection/artist-colla­bs.
